RelatedSentence: CCHP partnership will provide LISI agents and their clients with an expanded product portfolio , services and providers to all who live and work in the San Francisco Bay area .
, the premier California General Agency is pleased to announce their newly contracted partnership with Chinese Community Health Plan .
CHHP was created in 1985 , when Chinese Hospital obtained a license from the state of California , under the Knox - Keene Act , to develop its own community - based health plan .
After establishing an affordable premium rate and a group of physicians able to deliver culturally - appropriate care , CCHP began enrolling members in October 1987 .
